data.description: Welcome home to this well-maintained Avery floorplan! As you step through the front door you'll be greeted by a niche wall that adds tons of style and function. The heart of the home is definitely the expansive kitchen boasting a large center island with seating, a coffee bar, and tons of cabinet space! Flex room could be used as another bedroom or gym! Situated on a larger lot, the backyard is a blank space to create your own look. Two security screen doors were installed in the front and back!
